This reposity contains the java code I created while I was writing my posts about cucumber-jvm.

======

The first post is about the basics of BDD, cucumber and how to set up an eclipse project for executing cucumber features for java. You can find more about it here:

http://www.zsoltfabok.com/blog/2011/12/cucumber-jvm-preparation/

The second post continues where the first stopped and provides more information and technique how to use cucumber scenarios in Java:

http://www.zsoltfabok.com/blog/2011/12/cucumber-jvm-more-scenarios/


The third post shows how to use cucumber-jvm with spring and work with dependency injection:

http://www.zsoltfabok.com/blog/2012/01/cucumber-jvm-di/
